'''''Mandabi''''' (Igifaransa: '''''Le Mandat''''', "The Money Order") ni filime yo mu 1968 yanditswe kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Senegali Ousmane Sembène <ref>Mandabi (1968) | The Criterion Collection <nowiki>https://www.criterion.com</nowiki> › films › 29067-mandabi</ref>. Iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cya Sembène cyitwa ''The Money-Order'' kandi ni filime ya mbere y’umuyobozi mu rurimi rwe kavukire rwa Wolof <ref>Mandabi review: Wolof masterwork ripe for rediscovery - BFI <nowiki>https://www.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › sight-and-sound › reviews › m...</ref>. Kubera ko benshi mu baturage ba Senegal batumva igifaransa, Sembène yashakaga guhanga sinema kubavuga Wolof<ref>Mandabi review – Ousmane Sembène classic about ... <nowiki>https://www.theguardian.com</nowiki> › film › jun › mandabi-revi...</ref>. Iyi niyo filime ya mbere yuzuye  ururimi nyafurika kuva muri Afrika y'uburengerazuba<ref>Mandabi | film by Sembène [1968] | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › ... › Novelists L-Z</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Umuyisilamu wo muri Senegal udafite akazi, Ibrahima Dieng, abana n'abagore be babiri n'abana barindwi i Dakar <ref>Mandabi / The Money Order | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › the-money-order-mand...</ref>. Mwishywa we, Abdou, yohereje we kugira amafaranga kuva Paris agaciro 25.000 y'amanyarwanda<ref>Mandabi (1968) awards & festivals on MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › mandabi › awards</ref>, akaba yarakijjwe no gukubura mu muhanda<ref>Ousmane Sembene - Mandabi <nowiki>https://www.mtholyoke.edu</nowiki> › page20</ref>. Ibrahima akabika amafaranga ye wenyine, akazigamira mwishywa we, agaha mushiki we umugabane<ref>The Money Order: A classic of west African cinema - The Irish ... <nowiki>https://www.irishtimes.com</nowiki> › culture › film › the-mone...</ref>.

== Kwandika ==
Nyuma yuko iyi filime itari imaze imyaka igera ku bantu bareba sinema, yasubiwemo mu mwanzuro wa 4K maze itangwa mu iserukiramuco rya Lumière rya 2019 ryabereye i Lyon mu Bufaransa.  Muri Kamena 2021, iyi verisiyo yasubiwemo yerekanwe muri sinema mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]]<ref>‎Mandabi (1968) directed by Ousmane Sembène ... - Letterboxd <nowiki>https://letterboxd.com</nowiki> › film › mandabi</ref> .

